                        for a better web.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <ul class="nav nav-footer justify-content-center justify-content-lg-end">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="nav-link text-muted">Creative Tim</a>
                        </li>
